nodes.text: DNX-N1 was a planet located within the Wild Space DNX-N1 system. Charted but largely unexplored, it was the homeworld of the sentient gaseous species known as the Filar-Nitzan.

DNX-N1 was first indirectly mentioned in Alliance Intelligence Reports, a 1995 sourcebook for West End Games' Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game. The planet was first given its name by the 1998 sourcebook Alien Encounters. The 2009 reference book The Essential Atlas placed the DNX-N1 system, and therefore the planet DNX-N1, within grid square N-21.
